@startuml 决策审计交互时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "DecisionLogManager" as DLM
participant "LogExportService" as LES

User -> Frontend : 进入决策审计界面
Frontend -> DLM : get_all_logs()
DLM --> Frontend : 返回日志列表
Frontend --> User : 展示决策日志列表
User -> Frontend : 关键词查询并查看详情
Frontend -> DLM : get_log_detail(log_id)
DLM --> Frontend : 返回完整问答记录
Frontend --> User : 展示日志详情与检索语段
User -> Frontend : 导出日志
Frontend -> LES : export_to_csv(logs)
LES --> Frontend : 返回CSV文件
Frontend --> User : 下载导出文件

@enduml
